The paper deals with precoder designs for multiuser multiple-input-single-output broadcasting channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses power allocation and user-ordering algorithms, which are relevant to networked systems (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper proposes a new precoder design that improves upon previous designs, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.LG).
